      <title>俄罗斯报告乌克兰袭击后费奥多西亚港发生爆炸</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-12-26/russia-reports-explosion-at-feodosia-port-after-ukraine-attack</link>
      <description><![CDATA[俄罗斯报告称，乌克兰军队发动袭击后，克里米亚东部港口费奥多西亚发生爆炸，并引发火灾。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-12-26/russia-reports-explosion-at-feodosia-port-after-ukraine-attack</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 26 Dec 2023 05:11:14 GMT</pubDate>
