    <item>
      <title>越南官员因天坑蔓延而暂停采砂</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-12-26/vietnam-official-held-over-sand-mining-as-sinkholes-spread</link>
      <description><![CDATA[越南一个省份的负责人因涉嫌帮助一家公司非法开采沙子而被警方逮捕，部分原因是造成海岸线侵蚀和湄公河三角洲的污水坑——国家的饭碗。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-12-26/vietnam-official-held-over-sand-mining-as-sinkholes-spread</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 26 Dec 2023 04:05:28 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>无人机袭击造成军队受伤后，美国对伊拉克目标进行打击</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-12-26/us-strikes-facilities-in-iraq-after-drone-attack-injures-troops</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国军方对伊拉克境内的三个设施发动了袭击，目标是伊朗支持的恐怖组织，华盛顿指责该组织对美国人员进行了一系列袭击，其中周一造成三人受伤。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-12-26/us-strikes-facilities-in-iraq-after-drone-attack-injures-troops</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 26 Dec 2023 03:57:19 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>日本岸田计划成立新党组以帮助重建信任</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-12-26/japan-s-kishida-plans-new-party-group-to-help-rebuild-trust</link>
      <description><![CDATA[日本首相岸田文雄表示，他将于下个月在执政的自民党内成立一个新小组，负责在普遍未申报政治资金的指控后恢复信任。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-12-26/japan-s-kishida-plans-new-party-group-to-help-rebuild-trust</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 26 Dec 2023 03:45:05 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
