    <item>
      <title>内塔尼亚胡表示和平取决于哈马斯的终结和加沙非军事化</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-12-26/netanyahu-says-peace-depends-on-hamas-end-demilitarized-gaza</link>
      <description><![CDATA[以色列总理本杰明·内塔尼亚胡概述了在与哈马斯的战争中实现和平的三个先决条件：摧毁该组织、加沙非军事化以及巴勒斯坦社会“去激进化”。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-12-26/netanyahu-says-peace-depends-on-hamas-end-demilitarized-gaza</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 26 Dec 2023 02:42:13 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>金正恩将在其权力巅峰时期主持 2024 年关键政策会议</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-12-26/kim-set-to-helm-key-2024-policy-address-at-the-peak-of-his-powers</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于朝鲜军事和经济的进步，金正恩预计将主持一次重要的政策制定会议，并获得新的权力，这将使他能够顶住美国要求其放弃核武器计划的压力。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-12-26/kim-set-to-helm-key-2024-policy-address-at-the-peak-of-his-powers</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 26 Dec 2023 00:14:27 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>随着战争的加剧，以色列国防开支增加 80 亿美元</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-12-25/israel-may-increase-defense-spending-by-8-billion-next-year</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据以色列财政部称，随着针对哈马斯的战争愈演愈烈，以色列明年将需要增加至少 300 亿谢克尔（83 亿美元）的国防开支。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-12-25/israel-may-increase-defense-spending-by-8-billion-next-year</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 25 Dec 2023 14:10:47 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>内塔尼亚胡誓言扩大加沙战斗，埃及提出结束以色列与哈马斯战争的计划</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/en/news/thp/2023-12-25/egypt-floats-ambitious-plan-to-end-israel-hamas-war-and-create-transitional-palestinian-government</link>
      <description><![CDATA[开罗（美联社）——以色列和哈马斯周一对埃及结束痛苦战争的提议给予了冷淡的公开回应。但长期的敌人并没有完全拒绝该计划，这增加了采取新一轮外交手段阻止以色列对加沙地带毁灭性攻势的可能性。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/en/news/thp/2023-12-25/egypt-floats-ambitious-plan-to-end-israel-hamas-war-and-create-transitional-palestinian-government</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 25 Dec 2023 10:52:18 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>因人口贩卖调查在法国滞留数日的飞机飞往印度</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/en/news/thp/2023-12-25/a-plane-stuck-for-days-in-france-for-a-human-trafficking-investigation-is-leaving-for-india</link>
      <description><![CDATA[法国瓦特里（美联社）——当局称，一架因人口贩运调查而在法国停飞的包机周二早些时候抵达印度，机上载有 276 名印度人。这些乘客本来要前往尼加拉瓜，但在瓦特里机场内被困了四天，经历了一次特殊的假期磨难。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/en/news/thp/2023-12-25/a-plane-stuck-for-days-in-france-for-a-human-trafficking-investigation-is-leaving-for-india</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 25 Dec 2023 09:54:30 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
